column2: SELECT GN.distance, p.ra, p.dec,p.class,p.specObjID, p.objid, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,p.objid,p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z, pz.z as redshift, pz.zErr as redshift_error FROM SpecPhotoAll as p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) AS GN ON GN.objID=p.objID JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID=p.objID ORDER BY distance
